title: Coffee chocolate chip cookies
ingredients: ['225g butter, softened', '220g dark brown soft sugar', '150g granulated sugar', '2 eggs, beaten', '3 tablespoons coffee-flavoured liqueur', '375g plain flour', '3/4 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '3/4 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '500g chocolate chips']
